<main class="crop-workspace crop-workspace--step1" id="cropStepApp">
    <aside class="crop-side-panel crop-side-panel--left">
        <section class="crop-tool-intro">
            <h1>도면 정리</h1>
            <p>원본 PNG를 그대로 두고, 실제 제작에 사용할 영역만 자릅니다.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="crop-step-list crop-step-list--unified">
            <section class="crop-step is-active">
                <button type="button" class="crop-step__header" aria-expanded="true">
                    <span class="crop-step__number">1</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__title">
                        <strong>자를 영역 선택</strong>
                        <em>원본 유지 · 선택 영역만 저장</em>
                    </span>
                    <span class="crop-step__status">진행중</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__arrow">⌃</span>
                </button>

                <div class="crop-step__body">
                    <div class="crop-info-box crop-info-box--blue">
                        <strong>작업 방식</strong>
                        <p>
                            도면은 흐리게 처리하지 않습니다. 이미지 위에서 드래그하면 빨간 점선으로 자를 영역만 표시됩니다.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="crop-current-card">
                        <label>현재 도면</label>
                        <strong id="cropProjectName">도면 없음</strong>
                        <small id="cropProjectPath">새 도면을 먼저 생성하세요.</small>
                    </div>

                    <div class="crop-button-grid">
                        <button type="button" class="crop-secondary-btn" id="applyFullCrop">전체 영역 선택</button>
                        <button type="button" class="crop-secondary-btn" id="clearCropArea">영역 다시 선택</button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="crop-control-note">
                        <b>선택 조작</b>
                        <span>영역 내부 드래그 = 이동</span>
                        <span>우측 하단 핸들 드래그 = 크기 조절</span>
                    </div>

                    <button type="button" class="crop-primary-btn crop-primary-btn--next" id="cropSave">
                        자르기 적용
                    </button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="crop-step is-disabled">
                <button type="button" class="crop-step__header" disabled>
                    <span class="crop-step__number">2</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__title">
                        <strong>버튼 이미지화</strong>
                        <em>색상 추출 · 버튼 도형 생성</em>
                    </span>
                    <span class="crop-step__status">대기</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__arrow">⌄</span>
                </button>
            </section>

            <section class="crop-step is-disabled">
                <button type="button" class="crop-step__header" disabled>
                    <span class="crop-step__number">3</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__title">
                        <strong>구역 추출</strong>
                        <em>구역명 · 등급 지정</em>
                    </span>
                    <span class="crop-step__status">대기</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__arrow">⌄</span>
                </button>
            </section>

            <section class="crop-step is-disabled">
                <button type="button" class="crop-step__header" disabled>
                    <span class="crop-step__number">4</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__title">
                        <strong>구역 보정</strong>
                        <em>polygon 정리</em>
                    </span>
                    <span class="crop-step__status">대기</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__arrow">⌄</span>
                </button>
            </section>

            <section class="crop-step is-disabled">
                <button type="button" class="crop-step__header" disabled>
                    <span class="crop-step__number">5</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__title">
                        <strong>좌석 배치</strong>
                        <em>행 · 열 좌석 생성</em>
                    </span>
                    <span class="crop-step__status">대기</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__arrow">⌄</span>
                </button>
            </section>

            <section class="crop-step is-disabled">
                <button type="button" class="crop-step__header" disabled>
                    <span class="crop-step__number">6</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__title">
                        <strong>최종 꾸미기</strong>
                        <em>예매 화면 최종 확인</em>
                    </span>
                    <span class="crop-step__status">대기</span>
                    <span class="crop-step__arrow">⌄</span>
                </button>
            </section>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <section class="crop-canvas-area">
        <div class="crop-canvas-scroll" id="cropCanvasWrap">
            <div class="crop-canvas-frame">
                <canvas id="cropCanvas"></canvas>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="crop-side-panel crop-side-panel--right">
        <section class="crop-right-card">
            <div class="crop-right-card__head">
                <strong>원본 미니맵</strong>
                <span>현재 도면 기준</span>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-mini-map" id="cropMiniMapWrap">
                <img id="cropMiniMapImage" alt="원본 미니맵">
                <div class="crop-mini-viewport" id="cropMiniViewport" hidden></div>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-mini-help">
                미니맵은 원본 확인용입니다. 실제 자르기는 중앙 도면에서 진행합니다.
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="crop-right-card">
            <div class="crop-right-card__head">
                <strong>선택 영역</strong>
                <span id="cropProjectStage">도면 정리</span>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-result-row">
                <span>저장 크기</span>
                <b id="cropSelectionSummary">선택 영역 없음</b>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-result-path">
                <label>저장 위치</label>
                <code id="cropSavePath">/temp/seatmap/도면명/seatmap-image.png</code>
            </div>
        </section>
    </aside>
</main>
